sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant G as Gateway
    participant RB as Ring Buffer
    participant ME as Matching Engine
    participant L as Ledger
    participant K as Kafka
    participant A1 as Agent 1: Anomaly
    participant A2 as Agent 2: RAG
    participant A3 as Agent 3: Orchestrator
    participant R as Redis
    participant P as PostgreSQL
    participant Alert as Operations

    C->>G: Submit Order (suspicious)
    G->>RB: Publish Event
    RB->>ME: Process Batch
    ME->>L: Update Balances
    L-->>ME: Settlement Complete
    ME->>K: Publish Trade Event
    K-->>C: Order Filled

    par Async AI Fraud Detection
        K->>A1: Consume Event
        activate A1
        A1->>A1: Velocity Check
        A1->>A1: VWAP Deviation
        A1->>A1: Wash Trade Detection
        A1->>A1: Spoofing HMM Analysis
        A1-->>K: Anomaly Score: 0.75
        deactivate A1

        K->>A2: Consume Event + Anomaly
        activate A2
        A2->>A2: Vector Search (Qdrant)
        A2->>A2: Compliance Rule Lookup
        A2->>A2: Sanctions Check (OFAC)
        A2->>A2: User Profile Retrieval
        A2-->>K: Context Bundle
        deactivate A2

        K->>A3: Anomaly + Context
        activate A3
        A3->>A3: LLM Risk Assessment
        A3->>A3: Generate Risk Score: 0.82
        A3->>A3: Decision: FLAG
        A3->>R: Set Circuit Breaker
        activate R
        R-->>A3: Confirmed
        deactivate R
        A3->>P: Create Incident Report
        activate P
        P-->>A3: Report ID: INC-12345
        deactivate P
        A3->>Alert: Send Alert (Slack/PagerDuty)
        activate Alert
        Alert-->>A3: Alert Sent
        deactivate Alert
        A3-->>K: Decision Persisted
        deactivate A3
    end

    Note over C,Alert: Transaction allowed but flagged<br/>Future transactions may be blocked<br/>Incident INC-12345 created
